Cyber Claw/Quickstrike:




Cyber Claw dropped Rattrap's unconscious body, landing by the 
Predacon ship. She stayed a short distance, but not close enough to 
resort to a battle if they were too edgy for a friendly greeting. She 
watched the ship. 



Quickstrike, while on the roof of the Predacon ship, out for fresh 
air and a watchout, noticed a figure at the corner of his keen 
optics. He jerked his head around to it and watched. His mind 
immediately snapped: Dinobot! 

He went on defense. A Maximal was in the ship's range. But his 
scanners weren't picking up a Maximal signature, but a Predacon. He 
glanced harder at the figure. 

It was certainly Dinobot's structure. Another thing that didn't make 
sense was that form of Dinobot was gone. The original Dinobot was 
gone. Maybe it was another clone. 

Quickstrike clambered over to the open roof hatch from the ship and 
looked down into the beginning corridor. 

"Hey!" he called. No one was near him inside the ship. So, he opened 
his comm-link. "Somebody get down here!" he said with alarm. "We got 
uh Maxi outside here. Looks like Dinobot." He jumped down from the 
roof hatch into the corridor with a loud bang.
